1. Setup or Preparation Steps
  a. Create AWS account (Free tier)
  b. Create VPC
  c. Create an IAM role with Security Group
2. Creatre Cluster Control Plane
  Master--create with IAM role
    a. choose cluster name, K8s version
    b. choose region and VPC for your cluster
    c. set security cluster 
3. Create Worker Nodes and connect to cluster
  Node---EC2 instance
    a. Create as a Node Group (group of Nodes)
    b. Choose cluster it will attach to
    c. Define Security Group, select instance type, resources
    d. define max and min nuumber of Nodes (Autoscalling)
4. Create Worker Nodes and connect to cluster
    
